#######################################################################################################
##                                            Keybindings                                            ##
## These can all be changed by editing the files ~/.config/i3/config_keybindings,                    ##
## ~/.config/i3/config_workspaces and ~/.config/i3/config_window                                     ##
#######################################################################################################
## This configuration is focused on using only tilling mode, floating mode and multiple workspaces   ##
## No keybindings exist for Tabbed or Stacked mode, as well as no keybind to go back to Tilling mode ##
#######################################################################################################

# Start Kitty terminal
SUPER+t

# Kill focused window
SUPER+q

# Kill selected window
SUPER+Shift+q

# Switch between open workspaces
SUPER+Ctrl+Right
SUPER+Ctrl+Left

# Switch to a specific workspace
SUPER+number (for workspaces 1 to 10, pressing "0" to get to 10. Works with numpad as well)

# Resize mode for windows
## Use Up, Down, Left, Right while in resize mode to change the size of the selected window
## Esc or Return to exit Resize mode
SUPER+r

# Toggle (show/hide) the i3bar
SUPER+m

# Power Menu
SUPER+Ctrl+e

# Lock the system (Dracula theme lock)
SUPER+l

# Lock the system and go into suspend mode
SUPER+Ctrl+l

# Reload the configuration file
SUPER+Ctrl+c

# Restart i3
SUPER+Ctrl+r restart

# Open keybinding list
SUPER+F1

# Move window to scratchpad
SUPER+Ctrl+h

# Show window on scratchpad
SUPER+h

# Toggle sticky mode (floating window stays when you change workspace)
SUPER+s

# Move the window focus
SUPER+Left     focus left
SUPER+Down     focus down
SUPER+Up       focus up
SUPER+Right    focus right

# Move the window position
SUPER+Shift+Left     move left
SUPER+Shift+Down     move down
SUPER+Shift+Up       move up
SUPER+Shift+Right    move right

# Split new tabbed windows in horizontal orientation
SUPER+Ctrl+v

# Split new tabbed windows in vertical orientation
SUPER+v

# Enter fullscreen mode for the focused container
SUPER+Ctrl+f

# Toggle tiling / floating for focused window
SUPER+Ctrl+space

# Change focus between tiling / floating windows
SUPER+space

# Move a floating window around
Ctrl+SUPER+mouse click and drag

# App shortcuts (Works with numpad as well) 
SUPER+Shift+1 for Brave
SUPER+Shift+2 for Thunar
SUPER+Shift+3 for Thunderbird
SUPER+Shift+4 for SCRCPY with custom settings

# Power Profiles menu switcher (rofi)
SUPER+Ctrl+p

# Rofi menu for applications
SUPER+z

# Rofi menu for open windows
SUPER+Ctrl+z
SUPER+Tab
